<br>
I just paid 750 plat for a velium mask.  +8 wisdom I think.<br>
<br>
I would buy a Charred Guardian Shield.  Your group could do it in Sol A.  It's not too hard to buy.<br>
<br>
Get the shaman made idol for your range slot +2 wis.<br>
<br>
I got a Nashers or something like that arms.  It was about 800 plat and it would be an upgrade for you.<br>
<br>
You can always go velium for the rings too.  That will give you a couple points.<br>
<br>
