><font color=GREEN><font size=6><b>GREEK</b></font></font></center></a></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#e6ebd7><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/bthedruidsgrove.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=bindy>Bindy</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#333399>(5/24/02 10:11:30 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fthedruidsgrovedruidicequipment.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=26341.topic&index=4>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Upgrade Suggestions!</span><hr size=1> Well the following are totally get-able at your lvl (I know cos I have em and I'm same lvl as you hehe)  click my profile to see the stats on em...<br>
<br>
Face - Velium ruby veil (bought mine for 550pp)<br>
<br>
Head - Runed Circlet (drops of a mob in the King room in Perma (dont remember which) - not good if you dont like a head graphic... <br>
<br>
Finger - Diamond Wedding Band (drops of the groom of the wedding party - 4th floor of ToFS)<br>
<br>
Hands - Gnome Skin Gloves (drop off the guests at the wedding party, 4th floor of ToFS) - Altho... I'm looking to upgrade these myself now at 44...<br>
<br>
Shoulders - Braided Ivy Cords (Thistle Underbrush in LFay - or buy em, not too expensive)<br>
<br>
Legs - Kromriff Legs - (Quest: the final giant - quest version - is lvl 47, easily do-able with your group)<br>
<br>
Feet - Golden Efreeti boots (mob that drops em isnt killable at your lvl unless you go with a good group of 50+) but I got mine for 1Kpp<br>
<br>
Primary - Centi Warhammer (mine was a gift but they're not that much, about 300pp i think)<br>
<br>
Range - Seal of Thoridain (comes free with your 3rd Prayer Shawl - quest: I solo'd everything needed to obtain the ingrediants for the 3rd shawl)<br>
<br>
<br>
Good luck and happy hunting! :)<br>
